Class PrefixMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • PrefixMap

  • public class PrefixMap
extends Object
    This class briefly demonstrates how to create a custom data structure, and how to handle basic file i/o. There are two classes in this example: - PrefixMap.java - PrefixMapHelper.java - PrefixMapDemo.java Please note this class is designed to illustrate a specific concept, and may not be an example of good class design outside of this context.
    Author:
    Sophie Engle, CS 212 Software Development, University of San Francisco
